metadata.name: Variants #1: Wizard Supreme
metadata.description:
The Wizard Supreme was born with the ability to control magic at will. But don’t upset her, or that control becomes a bit shaky…just ask her parents, who no longer dare withhold dessert when she doesn’t eat her green beans! No matter her mood or the situation, you can always count on her to sport a piece of her favorite unicorn apparel.

Format: MP4
Length: 10 Seconds
Size: 2160x2160

Benefits:
2x Variants: Opportunity for random airdrops
5x Variants: Collaborative NFT utilizing your character(s) with secret benefits
Collaboration Holder: Ability to submit Variant Character recommendations (Names, traits, powers, etc.)
